3
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:21,600
Well, she bought the milk.

4
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:24,240
It's soy.

5
00:00:24,240 --> 00:00:27,040
This is why I do it.

6
00:00:27,040 --> 00:00:30,040
That's what I have to come home to.

7
00:00:30,040 --> 00:00:36,520
She probably won't be up for a few hours.

8
00:00:36,520 --> 00:00:38,520
This is going to be a very good year.

9
00:00:38,520 --> 00:00:40,520
Very good.

10
00:00:40,520 --> 00:00:41,520
Jan is at home.

11
00:00:41,520 --> 00:00:42,520
Jim is back.

12
00:00:42,520 --> 00:00:45,760
My protege, Ryan, is at corporate.

13
00:00:45,760 --> 00:00:46,760
Good stuff.

14
00:00:46,760 --> 00:00:51,160
Andy and Dwight are rocking the sales team.

15
00:00:51,160 --> 00:00:52,160
I feel very blessed.

16
00:01:22,160 --> 00:01:37,960
You know, generally it's not a good idea to click on any internet offers that you haven't

17
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:38,960
requested.

18
00:01:38,960 --> 00:01:41,120
