74
00:04:11,440 --> 00:04:13,520
Oh Michael.

75
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:17,400
One day Michael came in complaining about a speed bump on the highway.

76
00:04:17,400 --> 00:04:22,120
I wonder who he ran over then.

77
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:25,120
You ran over Meredith this morning in the parking lot.

78
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:28,920
And saved her life, yes, by taking her to the hospital.

79
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:31,040
