88
00:04:58,620 --> 00:04:59,620
Let me tell you something.

89
00:04:59,620 --> 00:05:01,620
Meredith ain't worth no 25 points.

90
00:05:09,420 --> 00:05:11,420
Maybe she hit me.

91
00:05:11,420 --> 00:05:13,420
You ever think of that?

92
00:05:13,420 --> 00:05:14,420
She hit me?

93
00:05:14,420 --> 00:05:16,420
I don't know whose fault it was.

94
00:05:16,420 --> 00:05:20,420
I wasn't exactly looking at the road.

95
00:05:20,420 --> 00:05:22,420
It's only Meredith.

96
00:05:22,420 --> 00:05:25,420
Yeah, it's only Meredith, thank God.

97
00:05:25,420 --> 00:05:28,420
