Yes, Jan is fine. Awesome, fantastic.

168
00:08:09,420 --> 00:08:11,420
Thank you for asking.

169
00:08:11,420 --> 00:08:12,420
Is the man in?

170
00:08:12,420 --> 00:08:16,420
So Ryan got promoted to corporate, where he is a little fish in a big pond.

171
