221
00:10:35,420 --> 00:10:38,420
Jumped in front of the car to get some workers' comp.

222
00:10:38,420 --> 00:10:40,420
I wouldn't put it past her.

223
00:10:41,420 --> 00:10:44,420
My girlfriend, who you have never met, your loss,

224
00:10:44,420 --> 00:10:47,420
is the only person I can ever imagine being with.

225
00:10:47,420 --> 00:10:50,420
We go together like topsoil and manure,

226
00:10:50,420 --> 00:10:53,420
