236
00:11:08,420 --> 00:11:12,420
Mix one capsule of omega fatty acid in with her kidney medicine.

237
00:11:12,420 --> 00:11:16,420
And you want to give that to her 15 minutes after she's eaten.

238
00:11:16,420 --> 00:11:18,420
And, oh, there's a fungal cream

239
00:11:18,420 --> 00:11:20,420
because she has this infection under her tail.

240
00:11:20,420 --> 00:11:22,420
So you're going to have to lift her tail

241
00:11:22,420 --> 00:11:24,420
and put the cream right at the base of her tail.

242
00:11:24,420 --> 00:11:25,420
Hey, Toby.

243
00:11:27,420 --> 00:11:29,420
Kelly, we're going to visit Meredith at lunch.

244
00:11:31,420 --> 00:11:32,420
Kelly?

245
00:11:33,420 --> 00:11:36,420
Well, Kelly's been so upset about Ryan dumping her

246
