248
00:11:41,420 --> 00:11:43,420
Please, go away.

249
00:11:44,420 --> 00:11:47,420
Okay, I have an announcement.

250
00:11:47,420 --> 00:11:48,420
You pushed Darryl out the window.

251
00:11:48,420 --> 00:11:49,420
No.

252
