253
00:11:50,420 --> 00:11:51,420
No, no.

254
00:11:51,420 --> 00:11:52,420
That is not funny.

255
00:11:52,420 --> 00:11:53,420
I love my employees,

256
00:11:53,420 --> 00:11:55,420
even though I hit one of you with my car,

257
00:11:55,420 --> 00:11:58,420
