258
00:11:58,420 --> 00:12:00,420
Look, I'm just trying to take everybody's mind

259
00:12:00,420 --> 00:12:02,420
off of this unavoidable,

260
00:12:02,420 --> 00:12:03,420
you know,

261
00:12:03,420 --> 00:12:05,420
I'm trying to take everybody's mind off of this unavoidable,

262
